其中一個成日講大話<br />\n<br />\n不過冇所謂，老豆老母知我有offer後好開心，彌補到dse時既錯誤，<br />\n加上而家冇朋友仲多左唔少時間追夢想，真正做到自己想做既野"},{"pid":"0b1da2ed4f9302930b920a2b3d3ffa0a0e0375cf","tid":238681,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:56:40.000Z","msg":"讀得asso緊係想升上去<br />\n咁佢升唔升到？"},{"pid":"8c6eedaa5f59abf15a8cc742d9b519188c2d48a7","tid":238681,"uid":38669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"關讀書咩事，我full time 番工，夜晚part time degree, 一星期番四晚，日日見到女朋友， 感情非常好，成績輕鬆3<br />\n重點係你地願意花幾多時間去同相方維繫"},{"pid":"b9dd3060bf0263dac450229de39f5e25bf2ad138","tid":238681,"uid":90303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀得asso緊係想升上去<br />\n咁佢升唔升到？</blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有fd上左莊 但無左個男朋友<br />\n其實無話臭唔臭雞 睇你自己點取捨姐<br />\n大家有大家既路 仲鐘意人咪試下箍煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6528df83806edb3868a148b5aa83fd9528d3177","tid":238681,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"話自己忙做籍口真係無撚敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係咪忙到飯都唔食？ 係咪忙到無做過非學業上既野先？<br />\n<br />\n唔分配好時間比另一半 你都唔係好愛佢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係無左先後悔下內疚下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1e3b11ff1ce533e5ee3a60c8d7dbbd64c7c49","tid":238681,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話自己忙做籍口真係無撚敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係咪忙到飯都唔食？ 係咪忙到無做過非學業上既野先？<br />\n<br />\n唔分配好時間比另一半 你都唔係好愛佢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係無左先後悔下內疚下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出到黎做野 你重忙呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal